      "rationale": "Fluent 2022R2 verified against ASME V&V 20 lid-driven cavity and Taylor-Couette benchmarks. Order-of-accuracy confirmed at 1.93 (expected ~2 for second-order scheme). Benchmark results archived and independently reviewed."
