      "rationale": "Three-level mesh refinement study conducted at the nominal operating point (5 L/min, 2500 RPM). GCI on fine mesh: 3.1% for NIH. Richardson extrapolation confirms asymptotic convergence. Mesh independence criterion satisfied at 4.2 million polyhedral cells."
