      "rationale": "Mean relative error across five operating points: 8.3%. Maximum relative error: 12.1% at the lowest flow rate (3 L/min), attributable to transitional flow effects not fully captured by SST k-ω. Errors are within the accepted threshold for MRL 2 comparative assessment."
