      "rationale": "NIH and RH index are the regulatory quantities of interest for hemolysis assessment per FDA guidance. Shear stress fields used as intermediate QoI for damage accumulation. Direct mapping from CFD output to RH acceptance criterion confirmed by regulatory reviewer."
