      "rationale": "SST k-ω selected based on documented performance for rotating machinery at Re ~ 10^4–10^5. Giersiepen power-law hemolysis model applied per published calibration for bovine blood. Model form uncertainty acknowledged and bounded by the 12.1% maximum relative error observed in output comparison."
