    "type": "DecisionRecord",
    "actor": "https://uofa.net/synth/actor/morrison-credibility-team",
    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed the required levels for MRL 2. Six factors are appropriately not assessed at this risk level. The CFD model demonstrates sufficient credibility for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device. Validation against in-vitro data shows mean relative error of 8.3%, within accepted thresholds. The model is accepted for the stated COU with the understanding that escalation to MRL 3 would require additional use error and sample characterization assessments.",
